{"tid":111740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講囇 台灣係咪繁體中國？","createTime":"2017-02-07T15:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T09:29:18.000Z","uid":60015,"like":84,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec9089b489c9db1ba0ffaa65f63647eab741c647","tid":111740,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:13:16.000Z","msg":"個人嚟講去過幾次台灣<br />\n覺得台灣同大陸基本上分別不大<br />\n污糟情況差唔多<br />\n黑心食品又多<br />\n啲人嘅質素都好撚差<br />\n講嘢都幾大聲 又多mk<br />\n而且識幾個台灣frd都幾撚無知<br />\n眼裏得日本美國<br />\n同大陸噴精冇乜分別<br />\n市容方面更加係垃圾<br />\n台北市又話幾大幾勁<br />\n屌你老母啲爛樓多到<br />\n又舊又污糟<br />\n嗰啲咩所謂周杰倫 小s住嘅豪宅個人覺得好麻<br />\n同居屋有幾分相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於好處都有嘅台灣人普遍鐘意睇書<br />\n書店開到成行成市<br />\n唔似香港咁生存唔到<br />\n而且台中台南人係幾熱情好客<br />\n政制嚟講都係民主選舉<br />\n<br />\n正皮:係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負皮:唔撚係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cddf0d72e33d53f09dbfa5e43299f824dc2fee7","tid":111740,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030fb62d15c1b18aa0957edbb07162b020cfeb55","tid":111740,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c12ce00ff9fb4fe2b114f3fd45dda8705362d18","tid":111740,"uid":17199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc9a8c946a58876e5f0981d44239a91583af802","tid":111740,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:26:45.000Z","msg":"香港一百步笑人地五十步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地點似支那都無香港咁多真正支那人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e2e